title: Thursday Pt2: Can Buccaneers turn season around? Ryan Fitzpatrick; Brian Dawkins
itunes:title: Thursday Pt2: Can Buccaneers turn season around? Ryan Fitzpatrick; Brian Dawkins
description:
Part Two of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and Super Bowl Champion Shaun O’Hara weighing in on how much faith they have in the Tampa Bay Buccaneers to turn their season around. Ryan Fitzpatrick stops by and talks about Lamar Jackson, the struggling Buccaneers and his gig talking football for Amazon Prime. Part two of the GMFB podcast finishes up being joined by Eagles legend Brian Dawkins.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
